{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Lien de reinitialisation de mail envoyé {% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <p>
        (en) If an account matching your email exists, then an email was just sent that contains a link that you can use to reset your password.
        This link will expire in {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.
    </p>
    <p>If you don't receive an email please check your spam folder or <a href="{{ path('app_forgot_password_request') }}">try again</a>.</p>

        <hr />
    
       (fr) Si un compte correspondant à cette adresse mail existe, alors un mail a été envoyé contenant un lien de reinitialisation de votre mot de passe.
        Ce lien expire dans {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.
    </p>
    <p>If you don't receive an email please check your spam folder or <a href="{{ path('app_forgot_password_request') }}">try again</a>.</p>
{% endblock %}
